headline: Jabil Set For Major AI Growth As Other Segments Falter: Analyst
summary: Jabil Inc. (NYSE:JBL) is set to report its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings on Thursday, September 25, with investor focus squarely on its outlook for fiscal 2026, particularly AI and cloud-related revenue. Bank of America expects the company to issue its usual conservative guidance for the year ahead, in line with past practice. AI and cloud demand is projected to remain a key growth driver in fiscal 2026, while other end markets are anticipated to stay flat or decline. Analyst Ruplu Bhattacharya

headline: Jabil Stock: Is JBL Outperforming the Technology Sector?
summary: Jabil has considerably outperformed the Technology sector over the past year, and analysts are highly optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
